@startuml Final Asset Saving & Publication

participant "VideoEditor\n(worker)" as VE
participant "RabbitMQ" as RMQ
participant "template-service" as TS
participant "media-ingest\n(MinIO)" as MI
participant "userservice" as US
participant "publisher" as PUB
participant "websocket-gateway" as WS
participant "Frontend" as FE

== Завершение генерации (всегда) ==

VE -> MI: upload final video
MI --> VE: mediaId

VE -> RMQ: AssetGenerated {mediaId, projectId, userId}
VE -> RMQ: NodeCompleted {nodeId, nodeType, workflowId, mediaId}

RMQ -> US: consume AssetGenerated
US -> US: CREATE GeneratedAsset (type=final)

RMQ -> PUB: consume AssetGenerated
note over PUB: bookkeeping — знает об ассете,\nPublicationRecord не создаётся

RMQ -> TS: consume NodeCompleted
TS -> TS: проверить граф:\nесть ли после nodeId нода autolist-publish?

== Сценарий A: autolist-publish нода есть в графе ==

TS -> RMQ: AssetReadyForPublish {mediaId, autoListId, projectId}
RMQ -> PUB: consume AssetReadyForPublish
PUB -> PUB: CREATE PublicationRecord {assetId, autoListId}
PUB -> WS: PublicationQueued {publicationId, assetId}
WS -> FE: SignalR → PublicationQueued
note over FE: карточка в "публикациях"\nсо статусом и прогресс-баром

== Сценарий Б: autolist-publish ноды нет ==

TS -> WS: AssetGenerated {mediaId, projectId}
WS -> FE: SignalR → AssetGenerated
note over FE: превью результата\n+ кнопка "Опубликовать"

FE -> PUB: POST /publications {assetId, ...}
PUB -> PUB: CREATE PublicationRecord {assetId}

@enduml
